OL,3,CHospitals Trust plan #160 million
OL,4,Cworth of cuts to plug budget gap
OL,6,Fspent #71 million more than expected
OL,7,Fover the last twelve months as a
OL,8,Fresult of rising costs, strikes and
OL,9,Fgrowing demand.JA new financial plan
OL,10,Faims to save #86 million over 2024/25
OL,11,Fand a further #80 million over 2025/
OL,12,F26, with the aim of breaking even by
OL,13,Fthe end of that financial year.JThere
OL,14,Fare few details yet on the cuts,
OL,15,Fbutsays it cannot rule out job losses
OL,16,Fto reduce its substantial pay bill.
OL,17,FSenior managers say any cuts made will
OL,18,Fnot affect patient safety.
