OL,3,CHospitals Trust plan #160 million
OL,4,Cworth of cuts to plug budget gap
OL,6,FOther cost-cutting measures include
OL,7,Freducing spending on expensive agency
OL,8,Fstaff, which has grown by 60 per cent
OL,9,Fsince the pandemic, and not always
OL,10,Ffilling positions when staff leave.Jt
OL,11,Fsays growing infrastructure costs for
OL,12,Fold buildings and the end of extra
OL,13,Ffunding during the pandemic, have also
OL,14,Fput it under pressure.JIt has a #1.7
OL,15,Fbillion annual budget ` the equivalent
OL,16,Fof #4.4 million per day ` and more
OL,17,Fthan 19,000 staff.JChief Financial
OL,18,FOfficer Paul Matthew said:
