OL,6,FChief Operating Officer Lisa Kelly
OL,7,Fsaid: "There is no doubt this is a
OL,8,Fchallenging plan.J"Looking ahead to
OL,9,Ffuture years so early may be common in
OL,10,Fbusiness, but as the NHS goes this is
OL,11,Fa real challenge."JChair Nick Carver
OL,12,Fsaid: "We want to be open to the
OL,13,Fpublic about the challenges we're
OL,14,Ffacing ` most of which are shared with
OL,15,Fthe wider NHS."JThe savings targets
OL,16,Frely on no further strikes over pay by
OL,17,Fjunior doctors, which are hugely
OL,18,Fcostly to hospitals.JSherwood Forest
OL,19,FHospitals NHS Foundation Trust, which
OL,20,Fruns King's Mill Hospital, also
OL,21,Fexperienced an unexpected #11 million
OL,22,Fdeficit over the last twelve months,
OL,23,Fdriven by similar factors.
